#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.standard\\_gamma"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a standard Gamma distribution."
msgstr "从标准伽马分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from a Gamma distribution with specified parameters, "
"shape (sometimes designated \"k\") and scale=1."
msgstr ""
"样本是从具有指定参数的伽马分布中抽取的，形状参数（有时称为 \"k\"）和尺度"
"为 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:6 of
msgid "Parameter, should be > 0."
msgstr "参数，应大于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:8 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``shape`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``mt.array(shape).size`` "
"samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是例如 ``(m, n, k)``，那么会抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 是 ``None``（默认值），当 ``shape`` 是标量时返回单个值。"
"否则，抽取 ``mt.array(shape).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:13 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的分块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:15 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则将张量分配在 GPU 上，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:17 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:20 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized standard gamma "
"distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的标准伽马分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.gamma`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:26 of
msgid ""
"probability density function, distribution or cumulative density "
"function, etc."
msgstr "概率密度函数、分布或累积密度函数等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:29 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:30 of
msgid "The probability density for the Gamma distribution is"
msgstr "伽马分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:32 of
msgid ""
"p(x) = x^{k-1}\\frac{e^{-x/\\theta}}{\\theta^k\\Gamma(k)},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:34 of
msgid ""
"where :math:`k` is the shape and :math:`\\theta` the scale, and "
":math:`\\Gamma` is the Gamma function."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`k` 是形状参数，:math:`\\theta` 是尺度参数，:math:`\\Gamma` 是"
"伽马函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:37 of
msgid ""
"The Gamma distribution is often used to model the times to failure of "
"electronic components, and arises naturally in processes for which the "
"waiting times between Poisson distributed events are relevant."
msgstr ""
"伽马分布常用于模拟电子元件的失效时间，并且在泊松分布事件之间等待时间相关"
"的自然过程中出现。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:42 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:43 of
msgid ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Gamma Distribution.\" From MathWorld--A Wolfram Web "
"Resource. http://mathworld.wolfram.com/GammaDistribution.html"
msgstr ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Gamma Distribution.\" 来自 MathWorld--A Wolfram Web "
"资源。http://mathworld.wolfram.com/GammaDistribution.html"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:46 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Gamma distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gamma_distribution"
msgstr ""
"Wikipedia，\"Gamma distribution\"，http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gamma_"
"distribution"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:50 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:51 of
msgid "Draw samples from the distribution:"
msgstr "从分布中抽取样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.standard_gamma.standard_gamma:58 of
msgid ""
"Display the histogram of the samples, along with the probability density "
"function:"
msgstr "显示样本的直方图以及概率密度函数："

